Adult.description: Rufous-winged Sparrow is duller than Rufous-crowned Sparrow, with mixed gray and rufous in the crown and without the white eyering or white mustache stripe. The lower mandible is yellow in Rufous-winged but gray in Rufous-crowned.

Breeding adult.description: Chipping Sparrows have a black line through the eye and lack the dark mustache stripe of Rufous-crowned Sparrow. In breeding plumage, Chipping Sparrows have a white stripe over the eye.

Nonbreeding.description: Chipping Sparrows have a dark, not rufous, line through the eye and lack Rufous-crowned's dark mustache stripe.
